      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that now. but it feels so predatory, like there are these tiny little things constantly snatching bits of my check before i can even make a dent in the actual loan. is there anything else besides the interest rate that causes that feeling of money just disappearing?",
      "source": "evaluator"
